  <script id="cf-head-scripts-polyfills" type="text/javascript">
  function cfAddPolyfill(option) {
    var scripts = {
      loading: {
        src: 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/loading-attribute-polyfill/1.5.4/loading-attribute-polyfill.min.js',
        integrity: "sha512-Kq3/MTxphzXJIRDWtrpLhhNnLDPiBXPMKkx/KogMYZO92Geor9j8sJguZ1OozBS+YVmVKo2HEx2gZfGOQBFM8A=="
      },
      intersectionObserver: {
        src: 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/intersection-observer@0.12.0/intersection-observer.js',
        integrity: "sha256-33xL9TzrOxUWT7HDl78oQFuiZ+xWQyfaTgZ57S9PCDA="
      },
      containerQuery: {
        src: 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/container-query-polyfill@1/dist/container-query-polyfill.modern.js',
        integrity: '',
      },
    };
    var selectedOption = scripts[option];
    var script = document.createElement('script');

    script.src = selectedOption.src;
    script.integrity = selectedOption.integrity;
    script.crossOrigin = "anonymous";
    script.referrerPolicy = "no-referrer";
    if (option === 'containerQuery') {
      // We need to add this because this polyfill was overriding jQuery
      // it still works when we revert the $ to be jQuery
      script.onload = function() {
        $ = jQuery
      }
    }
    var cfHeadScripts = document.getElementById('cf-head-scripts');
    cfHeadScripts.parentNode.insertBefore(script, cfHeadScripts.nextSibling);
  }
  if (!('loading' in HTMLImageElement.prototype)) {
    cfAddPolyfill('loading')
  };
  if (!'IntersectionObserver' in window) {
    cfAddPolyfill('intersectionObserver')
  };
  if (!('container' in document.documentElement.style)) {
    cfAddPolyfill('containerQuery')
  }
</script>

<script id="__cf_fetcher">

const originalFetch = window.fetch
window.fetch = async (request, init) => {
  if (init && typeof init == 'object' && init.method?.toLowerCase() === 'post') {
    if (init?.headers?.['X-CF2-POST-TYPE'] === 'submit') {
      init.redirect = 'manual'
      const csrfToken = document.querySelector('[name="csrf-token"]')?.content
      if (csrfToken) {
        init.headers['X-CSRF-Token'] = csrfToken
      }
    }
  }

  const response = await originalFetch(request, init)

  if (response?.type === 'opaqueredirect') {
    window.location.href = response?.url ?? window.location.href
  }
  return response
}
</script>

data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1223"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1224" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1225">Do I have to pay for updates?
</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1227" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1228"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1229"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1230" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">No! We give constant updates to our software, add new templates and you get it all for FREE! Because ClickFunnels is on the cloud, when we make an update or add new features, they automatically show up in your account!

</span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1232" data-accordion="header" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1233"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1234"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1235" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1236">Are my funnels secure?

</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1238" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1239"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1240"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1241" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">Yes! Security is our top priority, and we built ClickFunnels from the ground up to make sure your funnels, subscribers, and members area are secure. You don&#39;t have to worry about staying up-to-date with &#34;plugins&#34; that can easily be compromised.

</span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1243" data-accordion="header" data-show-only="none" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1244"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1245"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1246" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1247">How long are your contracts?</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1249" data-accordion="content" data-show-only="none" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1250"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1251"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1252" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">There are NO long term contracts or commitments. You can use ClickFunnels month to month, and cancel at any time you&#39;d like!
 
 </span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1254" data-accordion="header" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1255"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1256"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1257" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1258">If I have questions, is there someone I can talk to?
</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1260" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1261"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1262"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1263" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">Yes! We have a first class support team who can answer your questions 24 hours a day, 7 days a week! Just click on the &#34;support&#34; link on the bottom of any of our pages or go to <a href="http://help.myclickfunnels.com/" id="link-54597" target="_blank" class="elTypographyLink id-6Z-5JWR4-69" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:rgb(28, 188, 255);">http://help.myclickfunnels.com/</a></span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1265" data-accordion="header" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1266"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1267"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1268" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1269">If I cancel my ClickFunnels account, will I lose my data?</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1271" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1272"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1273"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1274" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">As with most &#34;software-as-a-service&#34; platforms, when you cancel your account, your data will become inaccessible, but don&#39;t worry, before canceling you have the opportunity to download CSV files of your contacts and members.</span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1276" data-accordion="header" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1277"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1278"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1279" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1280">Can I integrate my favorite autoresponders / shopping carts into ClickFunnels?</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1282" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1283"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1284"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1285" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">Yes, while we suggest that most people only use ClickFunnels to run your company, we also know that some of you have your own favorite tools you&#39;ve used in the past, so we integrate with most of the top service providers to make your funnel building process even more fun!

</span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1287" data-accordion="header" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1288"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1289"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1290" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1291">Do I have to install anything?

</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1293" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1294"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1295"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1296" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">No! We created ClickFunnels so you wouldn&#39;t have to have a whole I.T. department to run your website! Just login, start clicking, and you can build all of the pages in your funnel from the members area!




 </span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1331" data-accordion="header" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1332"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1333"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1334" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1335">   If I don&#39;t like ClickFunnels, how do I cancel?









</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1337" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1338"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1339"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1340" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">Simply login to your account, click on your account settings and click &#34;cancel my account&#34;. No need to call, email, or talk to anyone!
















 </span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1298" data-accordion="header" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1299"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1300"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1301" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1302">Can you handle the load?



</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1304" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1305"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1306"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1307" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">Yes! Because ClickFunnels is hosted on the largest public cloud cluster in the world (powered by Amazon and backed up by CloudFlare Security + CDN) we have virtually unlimited ability to scale in real time. Whether you send 100 visitors or 100,000+ today, it won&#39;t slow us down!






 </span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1309" data-accordion="header" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1310"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1311"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1312" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1313"> Who owns the data / content / subscribers?





</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1315" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1316"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1317"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1318" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">You do! Any content (including your users) is 100% owned by you. ClickFunnels doesn&#39;t have permission to use that content or contact your users for any reason. ClickFunnels is just a tool for YOU to deliver YOUR content!








 </span></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1320" data-accordion="header" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1321"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="SubHeadline/V1" class="elSubheadlineWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1322"><h2 class="elSubheadline"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1323" data-align-selector=".elSubheadline" data-slot-name="default"><span class="id-6Z-Xl9mE-1324">  Can I host the pages myself?







</span></span></span><i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-caret-down fas fa-caret-down"></i></h2></div></div></div></div><div data-page-element="RowContainer/V1" class="row id-6Z-Xl9mE-1326" data-accordion="content" data-slot-name="default"><div data-page-element="ColContainer/V1" class="col-md-12 innerContent col_left  id-6Z-Xl9mE-1327"><div class="col-inner"><div data-page-element="Paragraph/V1" class="elParagraphWrapper id-6Z-Xl9mE-1328"><p class="elParagraph" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true" data-mobile-line-height-linked="true"><span><span data-page-element="ContentEditableNode" class="ne id-6Z-Xl9mE-1329" data-align-selector=".elParagraph" data-slot-name="default">No, we&#39;re a hosted, &#34;software-as-a-service&#34; platform. We do this so that we can make sure you get all of the updates, new features, and so your funnels won&#39;t break. You can also export the HTML from any of your pages, as well as your contacts anytime you&#39;d like...

#stickyButtonSection {
	bottom:-100px;

  #customCodeHide {display:none;}</style><script class="id-6Z-EB6kPb-272">
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    let elementToWatch1HasBeenSeen = false; // To track if elementToWatch1 was ever visible

    function isInViewport(element) {
        if (!element) return false; // Skip if the element does not exist

        const rect = element.getBoundingClientRect();
        return (
            rect.top < window.innerHeight && rect.bottom >= 0 &&
            rect.left < window.innerWidth && rect.right >= 0
        );
    }

    function toggleButtonStyle() {
        const elementToWatch1 = document.getElementById('cta-home-hero-mobile');
      	const elementToWatch2 = document.getElementById('cta-home-hero-desktop-var');
      	const elementToWatch3 = document.getElementById('cta-control-hero-cta');
        const stickyButtonSection = document.getElementById('stickyButtonSection');

        // Check if either elementToWatch1 or elementToWatch2 is currently in the viewport
        const isElement1Visible = isInViewport(elementToWatch2) || isInViewport(elementToWatch3);

        // If either elementToWatch1 or elementToWatch2 is visible, set elementToWatch1HasBeenSeen to true
        if (isElement1Visible) {
            elementToWatch1HasBeenSeen = true;
            stickyButtonSection.style.bottom = '-120px'; // Hide modal while either element is visible
        } else if (elementToWatch1HasBeenSeen) {
            // If neither is visible but either has been seen before, show the modal
            stickyButtonSection.style.bottom = '0px';
        } 
        // If neither has been seen, there's no need to explicitly hide the modal here
        // since it's already set to hide while either is visible or has never been seen.
    }

    // Attach the toggle function to scroll and also run it once on load to ensure correct initial state
    window.addEventListener('scroll', toggleButtonStyle);
    toggleButtonStyle(); // Initialize the visibility state correctly on page load
});
</script> </span></div></div><div data-page-element="Button/V1" class="elBTN id-6Z-rnoPnx-308" data-liquid-replace="item" id="cta-home-testimonials-var" data-show-only="none"><a target="_self" href="#open-popup" class="elButton" aria-label="" data-disabled="false" data-show-button-ids="" data-hide-button-ids="" data-on-submit-go-to="" data-param-submittingText="Submitting..." data-style-guide-button="" rel="noopener"><span class="elButtonMain"><i class="fas fa-spinner fa-spin elButtonSpinner elButtonText"></i><span class="elButtonMainText elButtonText">Start Your Free Trial Today<i data-page-element="IconNode" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-angle-double-right" class="fa-fw fa_icon fa_apended id-IconNode fas fa-angle-double-right fas fa-angle-double-right"></i></span></span><span class="elButtonSub"></span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>

    <script>
  window.globalResourceData = {"hasCart":false,"resourceName":"site","expressEnabledPayments":[],"enabledPayments":["payment-card","apple-pay"],"enabledLegacyPayments":["payment-card"]};
  
  Object.assign(window.globalResourceData, {})

  // NOTE: global data should be compilled in yggdrasil-blueprints,
  // so we could refer below script there.
  // The main parts we use liquid syntax here are for "checkout_v2_state"
  // and "contact". We could shrink this script by simply assigning globalResourceData and window.sessionData
  // Therefore, this new global script inserted blueprint like could use import .ts files
  const productsById = {}
  const variantsById = {}
  const pricesById = {}
  if (window.globalResourceData.products) {
    window.globalResourceData.products.forEach((product) => {
      const { variants } = product
      const productId = product.id
      productsById[productId] = product
      return variants.forEach((variant) => {
        const { id: variantId, prices } = variant
        variantsById[variantId] = variant
        return prices.forEach((price) => {
          const { id: priceId } = price
          pricesById[priceId] = price
        })
      })
    })
    window.globalResourceData.productsById = productsById
    window.globalResourceData.variantsById = variantsById
    window.globalResourceData.pricesById = pricesById
  }

  window.cleanEmptyObjectKeys = (obj) => {
    for (var propName in obj) {
      if ([null, undefined, ""].includes(obj[propName])) {
        delete obj[propName];
      }
    }
    return obj
  }

  window.getSSRDynamicStoreData = (products) => {   
    
      const shipping = {}
      const billing = {}
      const billing_addresses = []
      const shipping_addresses = []
      const billingSameAsShipping = true
    

    return {
      mode: "guest",
      shipping,
      billing,
      billingSameAsShipping,
      billing_addresses,
      shipping_addresses,
    }
  }
  
  window.sessionData = {
      contact: {"session_created_at":1729726712314,"uuid":"7964b94f-ce0a-4f2d-a859-4d1200e98207","contact_affiliate_code":"0d90275722f3e60758d657547fc62c2e7af203b6f2b76dda0c6fa9fb31e054fd"},
      checkout_v2_state: "guest"
  };

  


</script>
